# Companion Unit Tests

Every *.ts[x] implementation file must have a same-named *.spec.ts[x] in the same folder for 1:1 coverage.

## Path Pattern
- frontend/**/*.spec.tsx
- backend/**/*.spec.ts

## Implementation Guidelines
- Create a test file for every implementation file
- Tests should be in the same directory as the file being tested
- Name test files with the same name as the implementation file plus .spec
- Aim for high coverage (80%+) for all business logic
- Test both success and error paths

## Example Structure
```
frontend/src/features/auth/
  ├── components/
  │   ├── LoginForm.tsx
  │   ├── LoginForm.spec.tsx
  │   ├── RegisterForm.tsx
  │   ├── RegisterForm.spec.tsx
  ├── hooks/
  │   ├── useAuth.ts
  │   ├── useAuth.spec.ts
```

